Pootle Authors
==============

These are people and organisations that have contributed to Pootle.

More detailed contribution statistics can be found on the GitHub's
contributor's page <https://github.com/translate/pootle/graphs/contributors>


Historical perspective
----------------------

Pootle was initially created by David Fraser for Translate.org.za.
Translate.org.za continued development.


Donors and funders
------------------

The Shuttleworth Foundation
Obsidian Systems
Open Society Institute
International Development Research Center


Major code contributors
-----------------------

Translate.org.za
Translate House
Evernote Corporation


